  "remarks": "PJSC ‘ZAVOD TULA’ is the main developer and serial supplier of mobile means of radiation, chemical and non-specific biological reconnaissance for the Unit of the Ministry of Defence of the Russian Federation in charge of radiation, chemical and biological protection. PJSC ‘ZAVOD TULA’ provides manufactured special radiation reconnaissance vehicles to the Russian Armed Forces, which are used in the war of aggression against Ukraine.",
